g.text: 8.2.4 Config vs Environment State impedance: The

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: namespaces used to partition the Config file, usually, will not

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: be ideal to partition the Environment. For example, suppose

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: that you have a DbEnvironment representing some arbitrary

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: database state. It would be natural to split that

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: environment by tables, so each namespace of environment

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: would be a table, but each component may touch multiple

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: tables, so the probe of environment and configuration do not

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: use the same namespace. In general the component must

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: know what environment namespace it must check.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - You need configurability, i.e., the behavior of the software

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: is not tied to the software, but what state it must produce

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - You need reproducibility, given the same Environment and

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: configuration you must achieve to the same state.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - You need test complex arrangements. If you need

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: configurability, testing that configurability can be very hard,

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: this architecture make that task manageable.
